  <!-- Modes -->
  <p class="section-label">GAME MODES</p>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="modes-list">
      <div class="mode-row">
        <span class="mode-icon" style="color:#00FFB4">@ CLASSIC</span>
        <span class="mode-desc">The standard experience. Five biomes. Watch life find its shape.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-row">
        <span class="mode-icon" style="color:#FF3296">% VOLATILE</span>
        <span class="mode-desc">Tripled mutation rate. Hazards twice as frequent. Genomes drift fast. Expect mass extinctions and sudden blooms.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-row">
        <span class="mode-icon" style="color:#C8C8C8">- DEEP TIME</span>
        <span class="mode-desc">Creatures live for minutes. Slow tick rate. Evolution is visible across real time. Watch lineages diverge.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-row">
        <span class="mode-icon" style="color:#64FF00"># OVERPOPULATED</span>
        <span class="mode-desc">Up to 2000 creatures. Resources thin. Competition constant. Structures matter more than anywhere else.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-row">
        <span class="mode-icon" style="color:#00C8FF">. VOID ONLY</span>
        <span class="mode-desc">A single biome. The empty dark. No shelter, no variety. What survives here truly earned it.</span>
      </div>
